title: LT Organic Farm Restaurant
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Family restaurant located on the LT Organic Farm. Menu is seasonal and uses freshly harvested veggies from own farm. Completely lactose free and gluten free with choices for vegans (please inquire). Walk ins are welcome but reservations are appreciated. Seating available inside and outside in the garden under gazebos. Pet friendly. Accepts cash and checks only. Host birthdays, weddings and other functions.
